    <title>Neural Architecture Search via Evolutionary Strategies</title>
    <summary>  We propose an evolutionary approach to neural architecture search
that leverages population-based training and novelty search to
discover architectures with superior performance on standard
benchmarks while maintaining computational efficiency.
</summary>
